{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"init"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"filename"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"writable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"writable"},{"text":" is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"true"},{"type":"text","text":", the mapped buffer may be modified, otherwise"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"it is an error to modify the mapped buffer. Modifications to the buffer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"are not visible to other processes mapping the same file, and are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"written back to the file."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that modifications of the underlying file might affect the contents"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MappedFile","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". Therefore, mapping should only be used if the file","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will not be modified, or if all modifications of the file are done"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"atomically (e.g. using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_file_set_contents()"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"filename","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the name of an empty, regular file, the function","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will successfully return an empty "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MappedFile"},{"text":". In other cases of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"size 0 (e.g. device files such as \/dev\/null), "},{"code":"error","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be set"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/FileError"},{"text":" value ","type":"text"},{"code":"inval","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"init","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"filename"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar","text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"writable","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"}],"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"title":"init(filename:writable:)","roleHeading":"Initializer","symbolKind":"init","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:4GLib10MappedFileC8filename8writableACSPys4Int8VGSg_SbtKcfc"},"abstract":[{"text":"Maps a file into memory. On UNIX, this is using the ","type":"text"},{"code":"mmap()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" function."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MappedFile"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/mappedfile\/init(filename:writable:)"]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MappedFile\/init(filename:writable:)"},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/MappedFile":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MappedFile"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a file mapping created with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_mapped_file_new()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". It has only private members and should"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"not be accessed directly.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MappedFile"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/mappedfile","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MappedFile","title":"MappedFile","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MappedFile"}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/MappedFile/init(filename:writable:)":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"filename"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SP"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"gchar","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gchar"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"writable"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"}],"title":"init(filename:writable:)","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Maps a file into memory. On UNIX, this is using the "},{"code":"mmap()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" function."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/MappedFile\/init(filename:writable:)","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/mappedfile\/init(filename:writable:)","role":"symbol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib","abstract":[]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/FileError":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/FileError","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/fileerror","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FileError"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Values corresponding to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"errno"},{"text":" codes returned from file operations","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on UNIX. Unlike "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"errno"},{"text":" codes, GFileError values are available on","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"all systems, even Windows. The exact meaning of each code depends","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"on what sort of file operation you were performing; the UNIX"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"documentation gives more details. The following error code descriptions","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"come from the GNU C Library manual, and are under the copyright"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"of that manual.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"FileError"}],"title":"FileError","kind":"symbol"}}}